  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What is the best way to restore my lost Yahoo toolbar?",
  "response": "To restore your lost Yahoo toolbar, follow these steps:\n\n1. **Check if the toolbar is disabled:**\n   - Open your web browser (e.g., Internet Explorer, Firefox, or Chrome).\n   - For Internet Explorer: Go to `Tools` > `Manage Add-ons` > `Toolbars and Extensions`. Look for Yahoo Toolbar and make sure it is enabled.\n   - For Firefox: Go to `Tools` > `Add-ons` > `Extensions`. Check if Yahoo Toolbar is listed and enabled.\n   - For Chrome: Go to `chrome://extensions/`. Ensure Yahoo Toolbar is enabled.\n\n2. **Reinstall the Yahoo Toolbar:**\n   - If the toolbar is not listed or is not working correctly, uninstall it first.\n   - For Internet Explorer: Go to `Tools` > `Manage Add-ons` > `Toolbars and Extensions`, find Yahoo Toolbar, and click `Remove`.\n   - For Firefox: Go to `Tools` > `Add-ons` > `Extensions`, find Yahoo Toolbar, and click `Remove`.\n   - For Chrome: Go to `chrome://extensions/`, find Yahoo Toolbar, and click `Remove`.\n\n   - After uninstalling, restart your browser.\n   - Visit the Yahoo Toolbar download page ([toolbar.yahoo.com](https://toolbar.yahoo.com/)) and follow the installation instructions for your browser.\n\n3. **Check for browser updates:**\n   - Ensure your browser is up to date, as outdated versions may cause compatibility issues with the Yahoo Toolbar.\n\n4. **Reset browser settings:**\n   - If the issue persists, consider resetting your browser settings to default.\n   - For Internet Explorer: Go to `Tools` > `Internet Options` > `Advanced` > `Reset`.\n   - For Firefox: Go to `Help` > `Troubleshooting Information` > `Refresh Firefox`.\n   - For Chrome: Go to `Settings` > `Advanced` > `Reset and clean up` > `Restore settings to their original defaults`.\n\n5. **Contact Yahoo Support:**\n   - If none of the above steps work, consider contacting Yahoo Support for further assistance. You can find support options on their official website.\n\nBy following these steps, you should be able to restore your Yahoo Toolbar. If you encounter any specific issues or errors during the process, feel free to provide more details, and I can offer more targeted advice.",
